do/weddings-bahamas" class="sf-depth-2 menuparent">Weddings</a><ul><li id="menu-11521-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/cakes" class="sf-depth-3">Cakes</a></li><li id="menu-11527-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/ceremonies-venues" class="sf-depth-3">Ceremonies &amp; Venues</a></li><li id="menu-11522-1" class="middle odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/flowers" class="sf-depth-3">Flowers</a></li><li id="menu-11523-1" class="middle even sf-item-4 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/formal-wear" class="sf-depth-3">Formal Wear</a></li><li id="menu-11524-1" class="middle odd sf-item-5 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/limousine" class="sf-depth-3">Limousine</a></li><li id="menu-11525-1" class="middle even sf-item-6 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/marriage-officer" class="sf-depth-3">Marriage Officer</a></li><li id="menu-11526-1" class="middle odd sf-item-7 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/photography" class="sf-depth-3">Photography</a></li><li id="menu-11528-1" class="middle even sf-item-8 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/video" class="sf-depth-3">Video</a></li><li id="menu-11520-1" class="last odd sf-item-9 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/wedding-professionals" class="sf-depth-3">Wedding Professionals</a></li></ul></li><li id="menu-11529-1" class="last odd sf-item-19 sf-depth-2 sf-total-children-18 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-18 menuparent"><a href="/things-do/worship" class="sf-depth-2 menuparent">Worship</a><ul><li id="menu-11551-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/anglican" class="sf-depth-3">Anglican</a></li><li id="menu-11550-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-3 sf-no-children"><a href="/things-do/assemblies-brethren" class="sf-depth-3">Assemblies of Brethren</a></li><li id="menu-11549-1" class="middle odd sf-item-